high_descs: walk forwards until you are just short of the end of the kitchen counters on your right, then turn left and walk to the kitchen counters ahead
grab a fork out of the furthest left pull out drawer of the kitchen cabinets
turn around and walk to the stove at the end of the room, then turn left and walk to the kitchen counter ahead
place the fork on top of the sauce pan on the kitchen counter top
grab the sauce pan off of the kitchen counter
turn around and walk over to the other side of the room on the right, and then walk over to the right side of the kitchen table there in the corner
place the sauce pan down on the kitchen table
anns.task_desc: place a sauce pan down on the kitchen table with a fork in it

high_descs: Turn left and walk up to the left side of the kitchen counter
Open the top left drawer and remove the fork from it
Turn right and walk over to the counter left of the oven
Put the fork in the pan on the counter
Pick up the pan from the counter
Turn left and walk across the kitchen to the round dining table
Put the pan down on the table
anns.task_desc: Put the pan with fork on the round table

high_descs: turn left, walk to the edge of the counter
open the first drawer, take the fork out of the drawer
turn around, walk to the stove, turn left, walk to the corner of the counter
put the fork in the pan
take the pan with fork in it
turn around, walk to the dining table
put the pan on the table
anns.task_desc: put the fork from drawer in the pan, move the pan to the dining table

high_descs: Move forward the turn to the left to go to the counter.
Open the top drawer and take out the fork.
Take the fork and turn left to go to the other side of the counter.
Place the fork on a pan on the right side of the counter.
Pick up the pan and fork from the counter.
Carry the pan and turn to the left, and then the right and face the white table on the left.
Place the pan on the left side of the white table.
anns.task_desc: Move a fork and pan to the table.

high_descs: Turn left, move to the counter, opposite the two plants, the end of the counter.
Open the left drawer, pick up the fork from the drawer.
Turn right, move to the counter left of the stove.
Place the fork in the pan.
Pick up the pan from the counter.
Turn left, move to the table, not near the chair.
Put the pan on to the table near the potato.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan containing a fork onto the table.

high_descs: Walk straight and turn left to the counter.
Open the drawer and take out the fork.
Take the fork and head to the stove.
Set the fork in the pan on the counter on the left of the stove.
Pick up the pan and fork from the counter.
Turn left and take the pan and fork to the dining table.
Set the pan and fork down on the table.
anns.task_desc: Take a pan and fork over to the dining table.
